&lt;p&gt;In this role, you’ll be responsible for both &lt;strong&gt;shopping and delivery&lt;/strong&gt;. Using the &lt;strong&gt;Buncha app&lt;/strong&gt;, you’ll shop customer orders in-store and deliver completed orders directly to customers.&lt;/p&gt;
